OL,3,CThe community that stepped in to help
OL,4,Celderly farmer targeted by fly-tippers
OL,6,FA farmer left 'distressed' and
OL,7,F'distraught' by a #40,000 bill to
OL,8,Fclear waste left by fly-tippers has
OL,9,Ftold of the life-changing support he
OL,10,Fhas received from members of the
OL,11,Fpublic, ITV News' Will Tullis reports
OL,13,FWe're stood in a farmer's field, amid
OL,14,Fpiles upon piles of waste that has
OL,15,Fbeen dumped illegally here.
OL,17,FAmid the 200 tonnes that has been
OL,18,Fstrewn across this field, we can see
OL,19,Feverything from mattresses, fridges,
OL,20,Feven children's toys.
