OL,3,CThe community that stepped in to help
OL,4,Celderly farmer targeted by fly-tippers
OL,6,FIt was fly-tipped here last year,
OL,7,Fmonths after the farmer who tends to
OL,8,Fthis land had turned 80, and shortly
OL,9,Fafter his wife died of cancer.
OL,11,FTo compound an already terrible year
OL,12,Ffor the farmer - who wants to remain
OL,13,Fanonymous - he faced financial ruin
OL,14,Fand was due to pay #40,000 out of his
OL,15,Fown pocket to remove it.
OL,17,FThat was until people up and down the
OL,18,Fcountry rallied round and raised the
OL,19,Ffunds themselves.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
