OL,3,CThe community that stepped in to help
OL,4,Celderly farmer targeted by fly-tippers
OL,6,FHis neighbour told us the help and
OL,7,Fsupport has been life-changing.
OL,9,F"My friend was just completely
OL,10,Fflabbergasted, gobsmacked at how
OL,11,Fquickly and how much money has been
OL,12,Fraised", said Will Dickinson, who is
OL,13,Falso a farmer.
OL,15,F"He has completely changed from being
OL,16,Fso distressed and so distraught at
OL,17,Fhaving to find the money himself to
OL,18,Fclear it up... (the money raised) has
OL,19,Fbeen transformational", he added.
