OL,3,CThe community that stepped in to help
OL,4,Celderly farmer targeted by fly-tippers
OL,6,FA fundraising page has now raised over
OL,7,F#55,000, drawing donations from far,
OL,8,Fwide and beyond the farming community.
OL,10,FOne donor said, "It is totally wrong
OL,11,Ffor the farmer to have to foot the
OL,12,Fcleanup bill, thank you for creating
OL,13,Fthis fundraising in his support"
OL,15,FAnother wrote: "It's nice to see there
OL,16,Fis still some good in the world."
OL,18,FBy law, farmers are responsible for
OL,19,Fall waste that is left on their land -
OL,20,Fand can be prosecuted if they don't
OL,21,Fremove it.
