OL,3,CThe community that stepped in to help
OL,4,Celderly farmer targeted by fly-tippers
OL,6,FSome in the sector told us this is
OL,7,Fhitting them hard at a time when
OL,8,Frising costs and needs to change.
OL,10,F"A victim of crime should not have to
OL,11,Fpay for the crime carried out",
OL,12,FCharles Hesketh from the National
OL,13,FFarmers' Union told ITV News.
OL,15,F"Farming's going through a lot at the
OL,16,Fmoment and this keeps getting worse.
OL,17,FThis is something they could really do
OL,18,Fwithout at the moment", he added.
