OL,4,Celderly farmer targeted by fly-tippers
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency has announced
OL,7,Fthe launch of a new specialist
OL,8,Fprogramme that will use drones to
OL,9,Fcombat fly-tipping.
OL,11,FThe NFU say this is a welcome move and
OL,12,Fa step in the right direction, but
OL,13,Fthey want to see more done to deter
OL,14,Fpeople from fly-tipping, including an
OL,15,Fincrease in prosecutions.
OL,17,FAn estimated 34 million tonnes of
OL,18,Fwaste a year is fly-tipped - enough to
OL,19,Ffill four million skips. It costs the
OL,20,Fgovernment around 1 billion a year to
OL,21,Fremove.
